title: Beauty Gurus vs Makeup Artists ft. Jackie Aina
description:
This week Manny and Laura have a very special guest: beauty guru, YouTuber, and entrepreneur Jackie Aina! They talk about how she started YouTube, the beef that makeup artists had with beauty influencers, her worst brand experience, her new fragrance brand FORVR Mood, and much more!
Follow Jackie on IG: @jackieaina
Check out FORVR Mood: https://forvrmood.com/
Follow Jackie on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/makeupgameonpoint/featured
Follow Laura on IG: @larlarlee
Follow Manny on IG: @mannymua733
